#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:64
msgid ""
"The easiest way is to set an entire object as smooth or faceted by selecting a "
"mesh object, and in *Object Mode*, click *Smooth* in the *Tool Shelf*. This "
"button does not stay pressed; it forces the assignment of the \"smoothing\" "
"attribute to each face in the mesh, including when you add or delete geometry."
msgstr ""
"最简单的办法是在 *物体模式* 下，选择网格物体，然后在 *工具栏* 单击 *光滑*/*平直"
"* 按钮，设定整个物体为光滑或平直。该按钮不会一直保持按下状态；该操作强制对网格中"
"的每个面指定 *光滑* 属性，继续添加或删除几何体也一样。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:70
msgid ""
"Notice that the outline of the object is still strongly faceted. Activating the "
"smoothing features does not actually modify the object's geometry; it changes "
"the way the shading is calculated across the surfaces (normals will be "
"interpolated), giving the illusion of a smooth surface."
msgstr ""
"可以注意到物体的轮廓仍然是棱角分明的。激活光滑属性实际上并没有修改物体的几何形"
"状，只是改变了表面着色的计算方式(对法向进行插值)，造成光滑表面的错觉而已。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:75
msgid ""
"Click the *Flat* button in the *Tool Shelf* 's *Shading panel* to revert the "
"shading back (normals will be constant) to that shown in the first image above."
msgstr ""
"单击 *工具栏* 中 *着色面板* 上的 *平直* 按钮，恢复为上面第一张图中的着色状态(法"
"向为常数)。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:81
msgid "Smoothing Parts of a Mesh"
msgstr "平滑部分网格"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:83
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can choose which edges to smooth by entering *Edit Mode*, "
"then selecting some faces and clicking the *Smooth* button. The selected edges "
"are marked in yellow."
msgstr ""
"另外，还可以进入 *编辑模式*，选择需要光滑的面，然后单击 *光滑按钮*，有选择地光滑"
"边线。被选中的边线显示为黄色。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:87
msgid ""
"When the mesh is in *Edit Mode*, only the selected edges will receive the "
"\"smoothing\" attribute. You can set edges as flat (removing the \"smoothing\" "
"attribute) in the same way by selecting edges and clicking the *Flat* button."
msgstr ""
"当网格处于 *编辑模式*，只有选中的边线能够接受 *光滑* 属性。同样可以通过选择边"
"线，单击 *平直* 按钮的方式设置边线为平直(移除 *光滑* 属性)。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:96
msgid "Auto Smooth"
msgstr "自动光滑"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst
msgid "Panel:    :menuselection:`Properties editor --> Object Data`"
msgstr "面板:    :menuselection:`属性编辑器 --> 物体数据`"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:103
#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:191
msgid "Example mesh with *Auto Smooth* enabled."
msgstr "开启 *自动光滑* 的网格范例。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:110
msgid "Normals panel with *Auto Smooth* enabled."
msgstr "在法向面板启用 *自动光滑* 选项。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:113
msgid ""
"It can be difficult to create certain combinations of smooth and solid faces "
"using the above techniques alone. Though there are workarounds (such as "
"splitting off sets of faces by selecting them and pressing :kbd:`Y`), there is "
"an easier way to combine smooth and solid faces, by using *Auto Smooth*. Auto "
"smoothing can be enabled in the mesh tab in the Properties Editor in the :ref:"
"`mesh-data-normals` panel."
msgstr ""
"仅使用上述的技巧，很难实现光滑面和硬表面结合的效果。尽管还有一些变通的法子(比如"
"选中并按下 :kbd:`Y` 分离一组面)，但使用 *自动光滑* 可以更简单的结合使用光滑面和"
"硬表面。可以在属性编辑器的 :ref:`mesh-data-normals` 面板的网格选项卡中启用自动光"
"滑选项。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:121
msgid "Edge Split Modifier"
msgstr "拆边修改器"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:123
msgid ""
"With the :doc:`Edge Split Modifier </modeling/modifiers/generate/edge_split>`  "
"a result similar to *Auto Smooth* can be achieved with the ability to choose "
"which edges should be split, based on angle. Those Angles are marked as sharp."
msgstr ""
"使用 :doc:`拆边修改器 </modeling/modifiers/generate/edge_split>` 可以通过基于夹"
"角选择需要分离的边线，实现类似 *自动光滑* 的效果。这些夹角可以标记为锐边。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:132
msgid "Edge Split Modifier enabled, based on angle."
msgstr "基于角度的拆边修改器。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:137
msgid "Edges marked as sharp."
msgstr "标记边线为锐边。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:142
msgid "Resulting render with sharp edge weighting."
msgstr "带有锐边权重的渲染结果。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:146
msgid "Smoothing the Mesh Geometry"
msgstr "光滑网格几何结构"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:148
msgid ""
"The above techniques do not alter the mesh itself, only the way it is displayed "
"and rendered. Instead of just making the mesh look like a smooth surface, you "
"can also physically smooth the geometry of the mesh with these tools:"
msgstr ""
"上面的技巧只是调整了网格显示和渲染的方式，而不改变网格本身。不同于仅仅让网格看起"
"来是光滑表面，使用以下工具可以本质上平滑网格的几何结构:"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:154
msgid "Mesh Editing Tools"
msgstr "网格编辑工具"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:156
msgid "You can apply one of the following in *Edit Mode*:"
msgstr "可以在 *编辑模式* 下使用以下工具:"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:158
msgid ":doc:`Smooth </modeling/meshes/editing/transform/smooth>`"
msgstr ":doc:`平滑 </modeling/meshes/editing/transform/smooth>`"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:159
msgid "This relaxes selected components, resulting in a smoother mesh."
msgstr "松弛选中元素，产生平滑的网格。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:160
msgid ":doc:`Laplacian Smooth </modeling/meshes/editing/transform/smooth>`"
msgstr ":doc:`拉普拉斯平滑 </modeling/meshes/editing/transform/smooth>`"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:161
msgid "Smooths geometry by offers controls for better preserving larger details."
msgstr "平滑几何结构，提供控制选项以更好地保留大的细节。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:163
msgid ":doc:`Subdivide Smooth </modeling/meshes/editing/subdividing/subdivide>`"
msgstr ":doc:`平滑细分 </modeling/meshes/editing/subdividing/subdivide>`"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:163
msgid ""
"Adjusting the *smooth* parameter after using the *subdivide* tool results in a "
"more organic shape. This is similar to using the Subdivision Surface Modifier."
msgstr ""
"在使用 *细分* 工具后调整 *平滑度* 参数，产生更加自然的形状。该工具与表面细分修改"
"器类似。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:167
msgid ":doc:`Bevel </modeling/meshes/editing/introduction>`"
msgstr ":doc:`倒角 </modeling/meshes/editing/introduction>`"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:166
msgid "This Bevels selected edged, causing sharp edges to be flattened."
msgstr "对选中边倒角，使尖锐的边线更加圆滑。"

