msgid "Modifiers"
msgstr "修改器"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:172
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can smooth the mesh non-destructively with one or several of "
"the following modifiers:"
msgstr "另外，还可以使用一个或多个下面的修改器，非破坏性的平滑网格。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:176
msgid ":doc:`Smooth Modifier </modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth>`"
msgstr ":doc:`平滑修改器 </modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth>`"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:176
msgid ""
"Works like the *Smooth* tool in *Edit Mode*; can be applied to specific parts "
"of the mesh using vertex groups."
msgstr "与编辑模式下的 *平滑* 工具类似，可以使用顶点组作用于网格的指定部分。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:179
msgid ""
":doc:`Laplactian Smooth Modifier </modeling/modifiers/deform/laplacian_smooth>`"
msgstr ":doc:`拉普拉斯平滑修改器 </modeling/modifiers/deform/laplacian_smooth>`"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:179
msgid ""
"Works like the *Laplacian Smooth* tool in *Edit Mode*; can be applied to "
"specific parts of the mesh using vertex groups."
msgstr ""
"与 *编辑模式* 下的 *拉普拉斯平滑* 类似，可以使用顶点组作用于网格的指定部分。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:182
msgid ":doc:`Bevel Modifier </modeling/modifiers/generate/bevel>`"
msgstr ":doc:`倒角修改器 </modeling/modifiers/generate/bevel>`"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:182
msgid ""
"Works like the *Bevel* tool in *Edit Mode*; Bevel can be set to work on an "
"angle threshold, or on edge weight values."
msgstr ""
"与 *编辑模式* 下的 *倒角* 工具类似，可以设置为基于角度阈值，或边倒角权重。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:189
msgid ":doc:`Subdivision Surface Modifier </modeling/modifiers/generate/subsurf>`"
msgstr ":doc:`表面细分修改器 </modeling/modifiers/generate/subsurf>`"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:185
msgid ""
"Catmull-Clark subdivision produces smooth results. Sharp edges can be defined "
"with :ref:`subdivision creases <modifiers-generate-subsurf-creases>` or by "
"setting certain edges to \"sharp\" and adding an :doc:`Edge Split Modifier </"
"modeling/modifiers/generate/edge_split>` (set to *From Marked As Sharp*) before "
"the Subdivision Surface Modifier."
msgstr ""
"Catmull-Clark 细分产生光滑的效果。可以使用 :ref:`细分折痕 <modifiers-generate-"
"subsurf-creases>` 或在添加表面细分修改器前设置指定边为 \"锐边\" ，然后添加 :doc:"
"`拆边修改器</modeling/modifiers/generate/edge_split>` (勾选 *锐边*) 来定义锐边。"

